history.content:
The Inclusive Excellence team under Prof. Grace O'Connell is looking for engineering students to interview for 10-20 minutes for a chance to win a $50 gift card. Our media and film will be shared across schools to expose a diverse range of students to engineering. 

 

If you’d like to share your passion and help bring in the next generation of Berkeley engineers, please fill out this interest form!

https://tinyurl.com/berkeng

For more about the Berkeley Engineering Inclusion Team, please visit: https://engineering.berkeley.edu/about/equity-and-inclusion/k-12-outreach/
